title: What can I do if my phone's music playback volume is small?
answer:
l   During music playback, press the volume up button to increase the volume.

l   Make sure the speaker is not blocked by the phone protective cover or other objects.

l   Play a ringtone (**Huawei Tune** in the ringtone list recommended) with high volume to check whether the problem resides in the music file.

If the problem persists, contact Huawei technical support or take your phone to an authorized Huawei service center.
